        "descriptions": [
          {
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "In the Linux kernel 5.11 through 5.12.2, isotp_setsockopt in net/can/isotp.c allows privilege escalation to root by leveraging a use-after-free. (This does not affect earlier versions that lack CAN ISOTP SF_BROADCAST support.)"
          },
          {
            "lang": "es",
            "value": "En el kernel de Linux versiones 5.11 hasta 5.12.2, la funci\u00f3n isotp_setsockopt en el archivo net/can/isotp.c permite una escalada de privilegios a root al aprovechar un uso de la memoria previamente liberada. (Esto no afecta a las versiones anteriores que carecen de compatibilidad con CAN ISOTP SF_BROADCAST)"
          }
        ],
